**JOINT CIRCULAR**

IMPLEMENTING SEVERAL ARTICLES OF THE GOVERNMENT'S DECREE NO. [136/2013/ND-CP](https://thuvienphapluat.vn/van-ban/tai-chinh-nha-nuoc/decree-136-2013-nd-cp-provides-social-support-policies-social-protection-subjects-315682.aspx "Decree of Government 136/2013/ND-CP") DATED OCTOBER 21, 2013 ON ADOPTING SOCIAL ASSISTANCE POLICIES FOR SOCIAL SUPPORT BENEFICIARIES

_Pursuant to the Government’s Decree No. [106/2012/ND-CP](https://thuvienphapluat.vn/van-ban/lao-dong-tien-luong/decree-no-106-2012-nd-cp-defining-the-functions-tasks-powers-and-organization-181850.aspx "Decree of Government 106/2012/ND-CP") dated December 20, 2012 on defining the functions, tasks, entitlements and organizational structure of the Ministry of Labor, War Invalids and Social Affairs;_

_Pursuant to the Government’s Decree [215/2013/ND-CP](https://thuvienphapluat.vn/van-ban/bo-may-hanh-chinh/decree-no-215-2013-nd-cp-functions-tasks-powers-organizational-structure-of-the-ministry-of-finance-226838.aspx "Decree of Government 215/2013/ND-CP") dated December 23, 2013 on defining the functions, tasks, entitlements and organizational structure of the Ministry of Finance;_

